replies.body:
I just use a simple batch file I created on my desktop;

> ping 104.160.131.1 -t

The NA game server is actually **192.64.170.1** (found on the [Network](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752674-Network-System-and-League-of-Legends-Logs) kb article), but Riot tightly controls pings to it so you'll frequently not get a reply. The server IP I use is a hop just before that and will respond normally.
